  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241114.htm", 
  "description": "近日微软Xbox部门负责人Don Mattrick参加了南加利福尼亚大学对于未来娱乐领域发展的探讨会，同时参与本次赛事的还有的电影行业的两位重量级人物:乔治・卢卡斯和斯蒂芬・斯皮 尔伯格.Mattrick表示Xbox One游戏主机上装备的新一代Kinect将会对未来娱乐生态环境带来革命性影响，未来都将使用手势和语音来控制娱乐系统。<b>对此斯皮尔伯格也赞同 Mattrick的观点，他说：“解放玩家的双手对于未来的娱乐系统的开发是有好处，让玩家能够体验更加身历其境的效果。”</b><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d45d93b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241114.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%AE%E5%B0%94%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9AXbox+One+%E7%A7%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%BF%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%84%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241114.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%AE%E5%B0%94%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9AXbox+One+%E7%A7%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%BF%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%84%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241114.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%AE%E5%B0%94%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9AXbox+One+%E7%A7%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%BF%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%84%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241114.htm&amp;t=%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%AE%E5%B0%94%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9AXbox+One+%E7%A7%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%95%