  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/241113.htm", 
  "description": "<b>感谢<a href=\"http://weibo.com/RiverRuns\" target=\"_blank\">Baserk</a>的投递</b><br /> 扁平化，本质是【布局】，呈现为两方面，即：<br /> A、弱化元素差异，让“层次逻辑”通过“排版”而非“元”来实现； B、强调“区域”边界，以应对海量内容（而早期拟物阶段，是强调“元”边界）。 这种本质，只是大屏触摸移动设备发展的『阶段性』需求。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d45d939/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241113.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%5D%E6%89%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241113.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%5D%E6%89%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241113.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%5D%E6%89%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241113.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%5D%E6%89%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241113.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%5D%E6%89%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td><td valign=\"middle\"></td></tr></table></div><br